

 Text Editors	Edit files with nano & vim. Save and exit (:wq). 

Action	Command

Write (save)	Ctrl + O → Press Enter

Exit	Ctrl + X (prompts to save if unsaved)

Cut Line	Ctrl + K

Paste	Ctrl + U

Search	Ctrl + W → Type term → Enter

3. Practice Task

Type: "Hello, Nano! Today is $(date)"

Save (Ctrl + O), exit (Ctrl + X).

Verify:
